  <brief_title>Procedural Pain in Palliative Care: Prevalence, Intensity and Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Procedural Pain in Palliative Care: Prevalence, Intensity and Treatment. A Prospective, Cross-sectional, Multicenter, National Study</official_title>
